ting-plan\";s:6:\"status\";s:7:\"publish\";s:4:\"type\";s:4:\"docs\";s:4:\"link\";s:75:\"https://help.codexpert.io/docs/woolementor/how-to-upgrade-my-existing-plan/\";s:5:\"title\";a:1:{s:8:\"rendered\";s:32:\"How to upgrade my existing plan?\";}s:7:\"content\";a:2:{s:8:\"rendered\";s:2442:\"<p>If you feel like upgrading your current license for our products, just follow the steps below:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Click on <strong>My Subscription</strong> from the <strong>Dashboard</strong> menu.</li>\n<li>Then click the upgrade button as shown in the screenshot.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-7252\" src=\"http://help.codexpert.io/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1205\" height=\"732\" srcset=\"https://help.codexpert.io/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/1.png 1205w, https://help.codexpert.io/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/1-300x182.png 300w, https://help.codexpert.io/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/1-1024x622.png 1024w, https://help.codexpert.io/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/1-768x467.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1205px) 100vw, 1205px\" /></p>\n<ul>\n<li>It&#8217;ll take you to the Upgrade page.</li>\n<li>On this page, there is an option to select a <strong>New Plan </strong>and the number of years you wish to pay the subscription fee.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-7253\" src=\"http://help.codexpert.io/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1149\" height=\"415\" srcset=\"https://help.codexpert.io/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/2.png 1149w, https://help.codexpert.io/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/2-300x108.png 300w, https://help.codexpert.io/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/2-1024x370.png 1024w, https://help.codexpert.io/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/2-768x277.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1149px) 100vw, 1149px\" /></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Now click the <b>Upgrade</b> button.</li>\n<li>You will be redirected to the checkout page and the adjusted amount of the upgrade will appear as shown in the screenshot below</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-7259\" src=\"http://help.codexpert.io/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/3-e1596617646711.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1159\" height=\"373\" srcset=\"https://help.codexpert.io/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/3-e1596617646711.png 1159w, https://help.codexpert.io/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/3-e1596617646711-300x97.png 300w, https://help.codexpert.io/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/3-e1596617646711-1024x330.png 1024w, https://help.codexpert.io/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/3-e1596617646711-768x247.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1159px) 100vw, 1159px\" /></p>\n<p>The usage amount on your current plan will be deducted and you will be automatically updated to the <strong>New Plan</strong> after completing the checkout process.</p>\n\";s:9:\"protected\";b:0;}s:7:\"excerpt\";a:2:{s:8:\"rendered\";s:325:\"<p>If you feel like upgrading your current license for our products, just follow the steps below: Click on My Subscription from the Dashboard menu. Then click the upgrade button as shown in the screenshot. It&#8217;ll take you to the Upgrade page. On this page, there is an option to select a New Plan and the [&hellip;]</p>\n\";s:9:\"protected\";b:0;}s:6:\"author\";i:346;s:14:\"featured_media\";i:0;s:6:\"parent\";i:1960;s:14:\"comment_status\";s:4:\"open\";s:11:\"ping_status\";s:6:\"closed\";s:8:\"template\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"meta\";a:0:{}s:12:\"doc_category\";a:1:{i:0;i:64;}s:7:\"doc_tag\";a:0:{}s:6:\"_links\";a:10:{s:4:\"self\";a:1:{i:0;a:1:{s:4:\"href\";s:49:\"https://help.codexpert.io/wp-json/wp/v2/docs/7254\";}}s:10:\"collection\";a:1:{i:0;a:1:{s:4:\"href\";s:44:\"https://help.codexpert.io/wp-json/wp/v2/docs\";}}s:5:\"about\";a:1:{i:0;a:1:{s:4:\"href\";s:50:\"https://help.codexpert.io/wp-json/wp/v2/types/docs\";}}s:6:\"author\";a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:10:\"embeddable\";b:1;s:4:\"href\";s:49:\"https://help.codexpert.io/wp-json/wp/v2/users/346\";}}s:7:\"replies\";a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:10:\"embeddable\";b:1;s:4:\"href\";s:58:\"